ote that we are unable to respond as quickly to letters sent in the post due to our remote working patterns.  As such we should be grateful if you would use our email address, Correspondence@giaa.gov.uk, quoting the relevant reference number where possible.\r\n\r\nMedia enquiries section\r\n\r\nFor all media enquiries, please contact the following address. Please note these contact details are not for use for public enquiries. \r\n","email_addresses":null,"phone_numbers":null,"post_addresses":[{"iso2_country_code":"gb","locality":"London","postal_code":"SW1A 2HQ","region":"Westminster","street_address":"1 Horse Guards Road","title":"Government Internal Audit Agency","world_location":"United Kingdom"}],"title":"Information requests, correspondence and enquiries"},"document_type":"contact","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-11-04T10:14:58Z","schema_name":"contact","title":"Information requests, correspondence and enquiries","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"514bc1d6-0913-4484-9dcf-f2ef540768ae","details":{"contact_form_links":null,"description":null,"email_addresses":[{"email":"giaa-communication@giaa.gov.uk","title":"Government Internal Audit Agency"}],"phone_numbers":[{"number":"0797 155 6035","title":"Media enquiries"}],"post_addresses":[{"iso2_country_code":"gb","locality":"London ","postal_code":"SW1A 2HQ","region":"Westminster","street_address":"1 Horse Guards Road\r\n","title":"Government Internal Audit Agency","world_location":"United Kingdom"}],"title":"Media enquiries "},"document_type":"contact","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-11-04T10:15:34Z","schema_name":"contact","title":"Media enquiries ","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D15","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/hm-treasury","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/hm-treasury","base_path":"/government/organisations/hm-treasury","content_id":"1994e0e4-bd19-4966-bbd7-f293d6e90a6b","details":{"acronym":"HMT","brand":"hm-treasury","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a37db09e5274a7908e352b4/s960_HMT_buiding_plaque.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/5a37db09e5274a79051c9235/s300_HMT_buiding_plaque.jpg"},"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"HM Treasury"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"HM Treasury","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/hm-treasury","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_roles":[{"content_id":"8477d658-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The GIAA Board brings together the Executive Management Team and non-executive board members.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-05-04T14:10:55Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Board Member","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8477d6fb-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Chief Executive is the Government Internal Audit Agency’s (GIAA) Accounting Officer. She is responsible to the relevant Minister and, as the GIAA is an Arm’s Length Body of HM Treasury, the Principal Accounting Officer of HMT for the GIAA’s performance.</p>\n\n<p>The Chief Executive is responsible for setting the strategic direction of the GIAA, in consultation with the advisory Board.</p>\n\n<p>Providing a service to the Accounting Officers of most of the major Whitehall Departments and over 100 other customers, the Chief Executive has stewardship of the vision for the Agency to deliver better insights for better outcomes. This is given effect through the Strategy 2023 and the annual Corporate Plan.</p>\n\n<p>The Chief Executive is also Head of the Government Internal Audit Function.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"board_member_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_u